{"tid":2035632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"參考西蘭公國，港人可集資到公海上自建平台立國","createTime":"2020-05-26T04:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T06:22:50.000Z","uid":254183,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ec9d1c7a809484a14833a99510ed4f28f62218fc","tid":2035632,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:52:59.000Z","msg":"買島冇用，只得業權而非主權，在公海上自建平台即可立國<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%A5%BF%E5%85%B0%E5%85%AC%E5%9B%BD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E5%2585%25B0%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%259B%25BD&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY6d04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=46e74e8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%A5%BF%E5%85%B0%E5%85%AC%E5%9B%BD</a><br />\n<br />\n西蘭公國宣稱其作為一個獨立的主權國家，合法性基於：<br />\n<br />\n位於國際公海水域範圍內:當派迪&middot;羅伊&middot;貝茨在1967年占領怒濤塔時，怒濤塔<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">位於國際公海水域範圍內</span></strong>，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">並不屬於英國或任何其他第三國的管轄範圍內</span></strong>。因此，西蘭擁有法理上的合法性。"},{"pid":"9506d26130ce076611e93a7ce728431256e6721b","tid":2035632,"uid":56084,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:55:59.000Z","msg":"做唔到既野唔好討論啦"},{"pid":"1d29ae721e90c39cc88b0996d45472ab79679f22","tid":2035632,"uid":25557,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:57:29.000Z","msg":"自己地方點解要走"},{"pid":"7af6732bfc7867561592eb42dbf3f96e92b0536b","tid":2035632,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d29ae721e90c39cc88b0996d45472ab79679f22","tid":2035632,"uid":25557,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:57:29.000Z","msg":"自己地方點解要走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:58:38.000Z","msg":"進可攻退可守<br />\n喺平台上生產軍火都得"},{"pid":"df6385276a67f2c2ea6de4b72d842ed818ddf0f2","tid":2035632,"uid":41873,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:02:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktHg23E.p